    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gods built this world, then left it to rot. Their once-gleaming spires have grown monstrous, a living prison made of endless, ever-shifting machinery. Smash your way out and reclaim your place in the cosmos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217790/extras/40c5bbaf6c23ca7d83a57b24ff0dface.poster.avif?t=1757364321\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217790/extras/40c5bbaf6c23ca7d83a57b24ff0dface.webm?t=1757364321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217790/extras/40c5bbaf6c23ca7d83a57b24ff0dface.mp4?t=1757364321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Smash Your Prison</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The walls are closing in. Literally. As the machine reacts to your presence, you'll learn to absorb and reflect its destructive power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wield Godlike Power</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wield Cathexis, a divine wrecking ball shattering the structure around you. Supercharge and ricochet your way to thundering, unexpected combos, upgrading your way to freedom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Morphing Megastructures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The living architecture has a mind of its own, and constantly reconfigures itself to throw new, dynamic challenges your way. You'll need both force and cunning to outwit its cruel designs. </p>",
